In the Matter of J.G.L. No. 20P09. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2009. Jayne B. Norwood, for Nash County DSS. Pamela N. Williams, Associate Counsel, for Guardian ad Litem.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 12th day of January 2009 by Respondent (Mother) for "Petition for Discretionary Review":

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 5th day of February 2009."
